# Daily content (gptoapk)

When the user says **写今天的**, **发今天的**, **今日内容**, **继续做 SEO**, **继续做 GEO**, or opens a `daily-content` GitHub Issue:

1. Read `content/queue/2026-Q2.json` + `content/queue/status.json` for **Asia/Shanghai today** (`node scripts/content-queue.mjs today`).
2. Full plan: `docs/content-marketing-plan.md`.
3. **Proactive:** If the user asks to continue daily SEO/GEO or set up automation, run the full pipeline for today without waiting for extra confirmation (commit + push unless they said not to).

## Reminder (方式 B)

- GitHub Actions **daily-content-reminder.yml** creates a `daily-content` Issue at **09:00 Asia/Shanghai** with today's checklist.
- User can also say **写今天的** any time in Cursor to trigger the same pipeline.

## Write (方式 A)

- Create `content/drafts/{date}-{locale}-{slug}.md` from `content/drafts/TEMPLATE.md`.
- zh: 1200–1800 字；en: 1000–1500 字；内链 3 条到 gptoapk 工具页与相关 `*-apk`。
- Integrate into `src/app/{locale}/blog/` (list + `[slug]/page.tsx`) matching existing post patterns.
- Run `node scripts/generate-syndication-pack.mjs` after draft exists.
- Same-day short video: add `content/video-scripts/{date}-{slug}.md` (9:16, 60–90s, 剪映用).

## Publish split

| Who | What |
|-----|------|
| **Agent / CI auto** | git push, Vercel, IndexNow, Baidu (cron), Blogger/Substack/Tumblr when secrets set |
| **User manual** | 知乎、CSDN、掘金 — copy from `content/syndication/zh/{date}.md` |

## After site publish

```bash
node scripts/content-queue.mjs mark published YYYY-MM-DD
```

Commit message may include `[syndicate]` to trigger optional external publish workflow.

## Do not

- Batch-publish 33-language thin translations.
- Full-text syndicate to third parties (summary + canonical link only).
